<div ana="b1" type="translation">
<p>On the 7th of Elul, year 3 + [1+] 1 [+1+?] =6[+?]<lb/>Abdadah to Ḥanniel to the
                    storehouse:<lb/>b(arley), s(eahs), 12<lb/>for w(heat), s(eahs), 6
                    [...];<lb/>Entry: to the storehouse of [Ma]kkedah: Ab[dadah] <lb/>b(arley),
                    s(eahs), 4; q(abs), 4 (and a) h(alf).</p>
</div>
<div ana="b1" type="commentary">
<p>This chit is unique because it records transactions not only at the "storehouse"
                    but also at the "storehouse of Makkedah" with exchange happening at the
                    storehouse and being deposited at the storehouse of Makkedah.</p>
</div>
